  "text": "Subscription Modification Policy\r\n\r\nThe academy offers multiple subscription plans including monthly, quarterly, semester, annual, and package-based plans.\r\n\r\nPlan Changes\r\n\r\nStudents may upgrade or downgrade their subscription plan only at the time of a payment event.\r\n\r\nExamples include:\r\n\r\n- Renewal payment\r\n- Package recharge\r\n- Subscription extension\r\n- Annual plan conversion\r\n\r\nMid-Cycle Changes\r\n\r\nSubscription changes are not permitted during an active billing cycle.\r\n\r\nAny requested change will become effective only when the next payment is processed.\r\n\r\nPricing Impact\r\n\r\nChanging a subscription may result in different pricing, discounts, package validity periods, and attendance limits.\r\n\r\nPromotional Offers\r\n\r\nPromotional pricing and discounts are subject to the terms applicable at the time of the payment transaction.\r\n\r\nThe academy reserves the right to discontinue or modify subscription plans without prior notice.",
